divs: Sighting DetailsWent outside to look for cellphone in car and saw three huge objects in V formation in the sky. Ran back into get my wife and kids so I didn't sound crazy. Ran in after they saw to grab wifes cellphone to take picture objects then took off very fast towards moon.
